## Config Directory Organization

### Key Configuration Files

```
config/
├── routes.rb                  # All application routes
├── database.yml               # Database settings
├── cable.yml                  # Solid Cable settings
├── queue.yml                  # Solid Queue settings
├── recurring.yml              # Recurring jobs (optional)
├── deploy.yml                 # Kamal 2 deployment
├── importmap.rb               # JavaScript imports
├── tailwind.config.js         # TailwindCSS config
├── application.rb             # Main app config
├── environments/
│   ├── development.rb
│   ├── test.rb
│   └── production.rb
├── initializers/              # App initialization code
│   ├── assets.rb
│   ├── filter_parameter_logging.rb
│   └── inflections.rb
└── locales/                   # I18n translations
    └── en.yml
```
